to low cost airlines, so EasyJet
versus [INAUDIBLE] versus Jet2

00:26:36.050 --> 00:26:38.270
versus Ryanair and all
the fees and the costs,

00:26:38.270 --> 00:26:40.770
and the pitfalls, and how to
maximize on all those airlines.

00:26:40.770 --> 00:26:43.310
So on the site we look
after that stuff as well.

00:26:43.310 --> 00:26:45.560
And like Brian says,
sometimes it just

00:26:45.560 --> 00:26:48.640
makes sense in cold hard cash
to be flying one way or another.

